The Glenn Beck Radio Show OCT-23-2013 WED     PODCAST





The Glenn Beck Program



         
      
      The Glen Beck Program - 10/23/13Wednesday, October 23, 2013 10:31 AM



The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET



Congrats to Glen, for his new baby grand daughter Lauralie is born! 


It's the blame game today and Glen analyzes why the left hates Ted Cruz

 and why they're blaming him for the drop in jobs numbers.


  Also, Chris Matthews is a sell out and a hypocrite, 
     telling Glen he's a big fan just a few years ago, and now 
       talks trash because his network changed directions.

  Plus, The Baltimore Ravens are being given millions in taxpayer dollars to promote Obamacare,

     Glen asks the question is it time to boycott the NFL?
